The ZEQ Framework is built upon the principle that physics, mathematics, and computation are unified through a fundamental frequency: 1.287 Hz (HulyaPulse), with a base temporal unit of 0.777 seconds (the Zeqond). This Work is released to advance open science, education, and truthful computation.

