SECTION 2 — DEFINED CONSTANTS

The following constants are intrinsic to this license and the Work:

  HulyaPulse   = 1.287 Hz       (fundamental heartbeat frequency)
  Zeqond       = 0.777 seconds  (base temporal unit / state-lock interval)
  ZEQ Origin   = DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.15825138
